*nagios-core-1.3 (19 Nov 2005)

  19 Nov 2005; Lance Albertson <ramereth@gentoo.org> files/nagios,
  +nagios-core-1.3.ebuild, -nagios-core-2.0b_p1.ebuild,
  -nagios-core-2.0b_p2.ebuild, +nagios-core-2.0b_p5.ebuild:
